pecial/Old Newsboys ed., published in Dec. of each year <Dec. 16, 1926-Dec. 1948>. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Description based on: 22nd yr., no. 27 (Nov. 1, 1921). Detroit times (Detroit, Mich. : 1958) (DLC)sn 96076539 (OCoLC)34383086"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:08.284Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-09", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-09"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn88063294/", "image_url": [], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [42.3329407, -83.0478365], "location": ["wayne", "michigan", "wayne county", "detroit", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-83.0478365, 42.3329407], "number": ["online resource", "1848", "2769-402x", "inp(nvf) cataloging region 5", "1", "microfilm service copy", "sn96076541", "library of congress", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn88063294/1940-12-22/ed-1/", "17777577", "sn96076539", "2025-07-01t13:40:48", "original", "2024-01-10t18:39:57.321128", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn88063294/1946-01-26/ed-1/", "university of michigan", "detroit public library", "sn88063294", "library of michigan", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Detroit times", "Detroit Sunday times"], "partof": ["catalog", "chronicling america", "serial and government publications division", "detroit evening times (detroit, mich) 1921-1958", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 70.53092, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "wayne", "michigan", "wayne county (mich.)", "detroit (mich.)", "wayne county", "detroit", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:26:17.806Z", "title": "Detroit evening times", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn88063294/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95070373/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn95070373", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/c46679b9-b94a-5fd9-b779-c272ac89c04e"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1995", "dates": ["[1995 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Daily Began July 13, 1995. Back issues available online. Print ed.: Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905). Mode of access: World Wide Web. Description based on: Aug. 18, 1995; title from title screen. Latest issue consulted: 145th year, No. 238 (April 17, 2019) (surrogate)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:34:05.793Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-03", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-03"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95070373/", "image_url": [], "index": 9, "language": ["english"], "location": ["wayne", "michigan", "wayne county", "detroit", "united states"], "number": ["2690-7186", "online resource", "2025-11-07t15:14:20.700000", "sn95070373", "33115544", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["catalog", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the detroit news ([detroit, mich.]) 1995-current [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 61.323586, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "wayne", "michigan", "wayne county (mich.)", "periodicals", "detroit (mich.)", "wayne county", "detroit", "electronic journals", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-27T08:50:05.467Z", "title": "The Detroit news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95070373/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2019201736/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/2019201736", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/a75bc0b9-b4b9-51ec-92f4-ab1f43e513f5"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1858", "dates": ["[1858 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Daily Print began with 1858. Issue for May 10, 1931 called: One hundredth anniversary edition. Editors: Wilbur F. Storey, Aug. 18, 1858-June 4, 1861; Henry N. Walker, June 5-Aug. 27, 1861. Due to strike on Apr. 15, 1962, combined with: Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905) and called: Detroit news-the Detroit free press. Due to a strike from July 15, 1995-Jan. 1, 1996, combined with: Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905) and called: Detroit news and free press. Saturday and Sunday issues combined with: Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905) and called: Detroit news and free press, Dec. 2, 1989-Apr. 30, 2006. Sunday issues include editorial page from Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905) and called: Sunday free press, May 7, 2006- Issue numbers v. 94, no. 120-v. 94, no. 265 skipped. Suspended Dec. 2, 1955-Jan. 16, 1956; Apr. 12-May 10, 1962; July 14-Nov. 24, 1964; Nov. 18, 1967-Aug. 9, 1968. Saturday and Sunday issues also have numbering for Detroit news. Other daily ed.: Detroit free press (Detroit, Mich. : State ed.). Weekly eds.: Detroit free press (Detroit, Mich. : Weekly), and; Detroit weekly free press; and: Weekly Detroit free press. Regional eds.: Weekly Detroit free press (Detroit, Mich. : Mich. ed.); Semiweekly ed.: Twice-a-week Detroit free press. Description based on: Volume 189, No. 64 (July 7, 2019); title from digital edition caption (freep.com, surrogate provided by publisher, viewed September 24, 2019). Latest issue consulted: Volume 189, No. 64 (July 7, 2019) (viewed September 24, 2019)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:01.189Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-15", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-15"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2019201736/", "image_url": [], "index": 10, "language": ["english"], "location": ["wayne", "michigan", "wayne county", "detroit", "united states"], "number": ["sn97063368", "online resource", "2689-0410", "2019201736", "2025-11-07t12:37:05.400000", "137343179", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Detroit news-the Detroit free press", "Detroit news and free press", "Sunday free press"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "catalog", "detroit free press (detroit, mich.;detroit, michigan) 1858-current [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 61.323586, "shelf_id": "Newspapers", "site": ["usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "wayne", "michigan", "wayne county (mich.)", "periodicals", "detroit (mich.)", "wayne county", "detroit", "electronic journals", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:57:39.303Z", "title": "Detroit free press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2019201736/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218642/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1933", "dates": ["[1933 TO 1933]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. XV, no. 21 (April 14, 1933); ceased with vol. XVI, no. 5 (Dec. 23, 1933). \"Independent.\" Cf. Ayer, 1967. \"Leading Negro weekly of Michigan.\" Merged with: Detroit independent, to form: Tribune independent of Michigan. Description based on: Vol. XV, no. 21 (April 14, 1933); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed March 14, 2018). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XVI, no. 5 (Dec. 23, 1933) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed March 14, 2018). Detroit independent Tribune independent of Michigan 2577-2570 (DLC) 2018218643 (OCoLC)1028674923"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:42.357Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218642/", "image_url": [], "index": 11, "language": ["english"], "location": ["wayne", "michigan", "wayne county", "detroit", "united states"], "number": ["1028641252", "online resource", "2018218643", "2577-2546", "2018218642", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "ori